#### 2.3.2 Measurements

**Widget Size:**
- Recommended: 5Ã—4 or 6Ã—5 grid cells
- Minimum: 4Ã—4 grid cells
- Padding: 16dp all sides

**Typography:**
- Year Number: 32sp, Sans-serif Bold
- Month Letters: 10sp, Sans-serif Medium

**Dot Grid:**
- Dot Size: 8dp diameter (much smaller than month view)
- Dot Spacing: 4dp between centers
- Row Height: 20dp (includes dot + spacing)
- Month Label Width: 24dp
- Gap between label and dots: 8dp

**Color Coding:**
- Past days: #1A1A1A (black)
- Current day: #FF6B35 (orange)
- Future days: #D9D9D9 (light gray, 40% opacity)

