**Measurements:**
- Widget Size: 2Ã—2 grid cells
- Ring Diameter: 120dp
- Dot Count: 52 dots arranged in circle
- Center Text: 24sp, Sans-serif Bold

---

## 3. App Interface Design

### 3.1 Design System Foundations

#### 3.1.1 Color Palette

**Primary Colors:**
```css
/* Light Mode */
--color-primary: #1A1A1A;        /* Text, filled dots */
--color-accent: #FF6B35;         /* Current day, CTAs */
--color-background: #F5F5F5;     /* Widget background */
--color-surface: #FFFFFF;        /* App screens */

/* Text Hierarchy */
--color-text-primary: #1A1A1A;   /* Headings, body */
--color-text-secondary: #666666; /* Metadata, labels */
--color-text-tertiary: #999999;  /* Disabled, placeholders */

/* Functional */
--color-border: #E0E0E0;         /* Dividers, outlines */
--color-success: #4CAF50;        /* Confirmation states */
--color-error: #F44336;          /* Error states */
```

**Dark Mode (OLED):**
```css
/* Dark Mode */
--color-primary: #FFFFFF;        /* Text, filled dots */
--color-accent: #FF8A5B;         /* Lighter orange for contrast */
--color-background: #000000;     /* Widget background (true black) */
--color-surface: #1A1A1A;        /* App screens */

/* Text Hierarchy */
--color-text-primary: #FFFFFF;   /* Headings, body */
--color-text-secondary: #B3B3B3; /* Metadata, labels */
--color-text-tertiary: #666666;  /* Disabled, placeholders */

/* Functional */
--color-border: #333333;         /* Dividers, outlines */
```

**Glassmorphism Mode (Pro):**
```css
/* Glassmorphism */
--color-background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15); /* Semi-transparent */
--backdrop-blur: 20px;                          /* Blur radius */
--border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);  /* Subtle border */
```

#### 3.1.2 Typography System

**Font Family:** San Francisco (iOS) / Roboto (Android)

**Type Scale:**
```css
/* Display */
--font-display-large: 72sp / 900 weight;   /* Widget date number */
--font-display-medium: 48sp / 700 weight;  /* App headings */

/* Headings */
--font-h1: 32sp / 700 weight;              /* Page titles */
--font-h2: 24sp / 700 weight;              /* Section titles */
--font-h3: 20sp / 600 weight;              /* Card titles */

/* Body */
--font-body-large: 16sp / 400 weight;      /* Primary text */
--font-body-medium: 14sp / 400 weight;     /* Secondary text */
--font-body-small: 12sp / 400 weight;      /* Captions */

/* Labels */
--font-label-large: 14sp / 500 weight;     /* Buttons */
--font-label-medium: 12sp / 500 weight;    /* Small buttons */
--font-label-small: 10sp / 500 weight;     /* Tags, badges */
```

**Line Height:**
- Display: 1.0 (tight for large numbers)
- Headings: 1.2
- Body: 1.5
- Labels: 1.2

#### 3.1.3 Spacing System (8dp Grid)

```css
/* Spacing Scale */
--space-4xs: 2dp;   /* Tight spacing */
--space-3xs: 4dp;   /* Minimal gap */
--space-2xs: 8dp;   /* Standard small */
--space-xs: 12dp;   /* Small */
--space-sm: 16dp;   /* Medium-small */
--space-md: 24dp;   /* Medium */
--space-lg: 32dp;   /* Large */
--space-xl: 48dp;   /* Extra large */
--space-2xl: 64dp;  /* Huge */
--space-3xl: 96dp;  /* Massive */
```

**Usage Guidelines:**
- **Component Padding:** 16dp (sm) as default
- **Section Gaps:** 24dp (md) between major sections
- **Screen Margins:** 16dp on phone, 24dp on tablet
- **Card Internal Spacing:** 16dp padding
- **List Item Height:** 56dp minimum (touch target)

#### 3.1.4 Corner Radius

```css
/* Border Radius */
--radius-sm: 8dp;    /* Small cards, buttons */
--radius-md: 12dp;   /* Default cards */
--radius-lg: 16dp;   /* Large cards, modals */
--radius-xl: 24dp;   /* Bottom sheets */
--radius-full: 999dp; /* Pills, dots */
```

