```

#### 3.2.2 Component Specifications

**App Bar:**
- Height: 56dp
- Background: Transparent (shows through to screen background)
- Hamburger Icon: 24dp, left-aligned, 16dp margin
- Title: 20sp, Sans-serif Medium
- [+ New] Button: 
  - Icon: 24dp
  - Padding: 8dp all sides
  - Background: Accent color (#FF6B35)
  - Corner Radius: 8dp
  - Right margin: 16dp

**Tab Bar:**
- Height: 48dp
- Tab Label: 14sp, Sans-serif Medium
- Indicator: 2dp height, full width, accent color
- Tab Padding: 12dp horizontal

**Widget Card:**
- Width: Fill parent (minus 32dp horizontal margin)
- Height: Auto (min 200dp)
- Background: #FFFFFF (Light) / #1A1A1A (Dark)
- Corner Radius: 12dp
- Elevation: 2dp (subtle shadow)
- Padding: 16dp all sides

**Widget Preview Thumbnail:**
- Width: Fill card width
- Height: 160dp
- Background: Widget background color
- Corner Radius: 8dp
- Actual rendered widget (scaled down)

**Widget Card Text:**
- Title: 14sp, Sans-serif Medium, color-text-primary
- Subtitle: 12sp, Sans-serif Regular, color-text-secondary
- Metadata: 10sp, Sans-serif Regular, color-text-tertiary

**Action Buttons:**
- [Edit] Button:
  - Style: Text button
  - Label: 14sp, color-accent
  - Padding: 8dp vertical, 12dp horizontal
- [â‹®] Menu Button:
  - Icon: 24dp
  - Padding: 8dp

**Empty State:**
- Illustration: 200dp Ã— 200dp, centered
- Title: 20sp, Sans-serif Medium
- Subtitle: 14sp, Sans-serif Regular, color-text-secondary
- CTA Button: Filled button, accent color, 48dp height

