#### 3.3.2 Component Details

**Live Preview Container:**
- Background: Matches widget background color
- Border: 1dp, #E0E0E0 (light) / #333333 (dark)
- Corner Radius: 12dp
- Padding: 16dp
- Shadow: None (flat design)
- Content: Actual RemoteViews rendered at scale

**Section Headers:**
- Font: 16sp, Sans-serif Medium
- Color: color-text-primary
- Margin: 24dp top, 16dp bottom
- Optional: Left border accent (2dp, accent color)

**Dropdowns:**
- Height: 48dp
- Background: color-surface
- Border: 1dp, color-border
- Corner Radius: 8dp
- Padding: 12dp horizontal
- Label: 14sp, Sans-serif Regular
- Icon: 20dp chevron-down, right-aligned

**Sliders:**
- Track Height: 4dp
- Thumb Size: 20dp diameter
- Active Color: color-accent
- Inactive Color: color-border
- Label: 12sp, right-aligned, shows current value
- Min Width: 200dp

**Radio Buttons:**
- Size: 20dp
- Spacing: 16dp between options
- Label: 14sp, Sans-serif Regular
- Layout: Horizontal (if space) or Vertical

**Color Pickers:**
- Color Swatch: 32dp Ã— 32dp, rounded 6dp
- Border: 1dp, color-border
- Label: 12sp, left of swatch
- Tap â†’ Opens color picker dialog

---

