**Primary CTA Button:**
- Height: 56dp
- Width: Fill parent (minus 32dp margin)
- Background: Accent color (#FF6B35)
- Text: 16sp, Sans-serif Medium, white
- Corner Radius: 12dp
- Elevation: 4dp

---

## 4. Interaction Design

### 4.1 Touch Targets & Gestures

**Minimum Touch Targets:**
- Buttons: 48dp Ã— 48dp (Material Design standard)
- List Items: 56dp height
- Cards: Full card tappable (min 48dp height)

**Gesture Support:**
- **Tap:** Primary action (select, open, toggle)
- **Long Press:** Secondary actions (context menu, reorder)
- **Swipe:** Delete (in lists), navigate (between months)
- **Pinch/Zoom:** Not supported (static widget sizes)
- **Drag:** Reorder emoji rules (with haptic feedback)

### 4.2 Animations & Transitions

**Principles:**
- **Duration:** 200-300ms (Material Design standard)
- **Easing:** Cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.2, 1) for most transitions
- **Purpose:** Provide feedback, show relationships, maintain context

**Specific Animations:**

1. **Widget Preview Updates:**
   - Type: Cross-fade
   - Duration: 200ms
   - Trigger: Any config change

2. **Screen Transitions:**
   - Type: Shared element transition (preview thumbnail â†’ full editor)
   - Duration: 300ms
   - Easing: Deceleration

3. **Button Press:**
   - Type: Scale down (0.95x) + ripple effect
   - Duration: 100ms press, 200ms release
   - Color: Accent color at 20% opacity

4. **Dialog Appearance:**
   - Type: Fade + scale (from 0.9x to 1.0x)
   - Duration: 250ms
   - Background dim: Fade to 40% black

5. **Slider Movement:**
   - Type: Immediate (no animation)
   - Haptic: Light impact every 10% (iOS) / tick (Android)

6. **Widget Add to Home:**
   - Type: Scale up from touch point
   - Duration: 300ms
   - Haptic: Success feedback

---

## 5. Responsive Design

### 5.1 Screen Size Adaptation

**Phone (Portrait - Primary Target):**
- Screen Width: 360-414dp
- Widget Gallery: 1 column
- Theme Gallery: 3 columns
- Widget Editor: Full-width preview

**Phone (Landscape):**
- Widget Gallery: 2 columns (if width > 600dp)
- Widget Editor: Preview left, controls right (split view)

**Tablet (7-10 inches):**
- Screen Width: 600-840dp
- Widget Gallery: 2 columns
- Theme Gallery: 4-5 columns
- Increased margins: 24dp

**Tablet (10+ inches):**
- Screen Width: 840dp+
- Master-Detail layout (gallery + editor side-by-side)
- Theme Gallery: 6+ columns

### 5.2 Widget Size Variants

**Year View:**
- 4Ã—3: Minimal (compressed dots)
- 4Ã—4: Comfortable
- 5Ã—4: Spacious
- 6Ã—5: Luxurious (recommended)

**Month View:**
- 3Ã—3: Tight (minimal spacing)
- 4Ã—3: Comfortable
- 4Ã—4: Spacious (recommended)
- 5Ã—4: Luxurious

**Progress:**
- 2Ã—1: Minimal (bar only)
- 3Ã—1: Comfortable (bar + small label)
- 4Ã—1: Spacious (recommended)
- 2Ã—2: Ring style

---

## 6. Accessibility Specifications

### 6.1 Color Contrast

**WCAG AA Compliance (4.5:1 ratio minimum for text):**

| Element | Foreground | Background | Contrast Ratio |
|---------|-----------|------------|----------------|
| Primary Text | #1A1A1A | #F5F5F5 | 14.1:1 âœ“ |
| Secondary Text | #666666 | #F5F5F5 | 5.2:1 âœ“ |
| Accent on White | #FF6B35 | #FFFFFF | 3.5:1 âš ï¸ |
| Dark Mode Text | #FFFFFF | #1A1A1A | 14.1:1 âœ“ |

**Fixes for Low Contrast:**
- Accent color on white fails AA for small text
- Solution: Darken to #D95225 for text (contrast: 4.7:1 âœ“)
- Keep #FF6B35 for large elements (dots, buttons)

### 6.2 Screen Reader Support

**Content Descriptions:**

```kotlin
// Widget dots
"January 15, 2026 - Birthday - marked with cake emoji"
"January 11, 2026 - Today"
"January 10, 2026 - Past date"
"January 12, 2026 - Future date"

// Sliders
"Dot size: 4 density-independent pixels, adjustable from 2 to 8"
"Dot spacing: 2 density-independent pixels, adjustable from 1 to 6"

// Buttons
"Add new widget"
"Edit widget configuration"
"Delete emoji rule"
"Unlock Pro features for $5.99"
```

**Focus Order:**
- Logical top-to-bottom, left-to-right
- Grouped related elements (emoji + label + actions)
- Skip decorative elements

### 6.3 Large Text Support

**Dynamic Type Scaling:**
- Support up to 200% text scaling (Android Accessibility Settings)
- Minimum font sizes remain readable at max scale:
  - 72sp display â†’ 144sp (still fits on screen)
  - 14sp body â†’ 28sp
  - 10sp caption â†’ 20sp

**Layout Adjustments:**
- Switch to vertical layouts when text wraps
- Increase touch targets proportionally
- Allow horizontal scrolling if needed

### 6.4 Motion Sensitivity

**Reduced Motion Mode:**
- Disable all non-essential animations
- Keep critical feedback (button press ripple)
- Replace fades with instant transitions
- Respect system `prefers-reduced-motion` setting

