## 8. Design Checklist (Before Handoff to Development)

### 8.1 Completeness

- [ ] All screens designed (Light + Dark modes)
- [ ] All widget types rendered at 3+ sizes
- [ ] All 12 preset themes visualized
- [ ] Empty states designed
- [ ] Error states designed
- [ ] Loading states designed
- [ ] Success/confirmation states designed

### 8.2 Specifications

- [ ] All measurements documented (dp/sp)
- [ ] All colors defined (hex codes)
- [ ] All fonts specified (family, weight, size)
- [ ] All spacing values marked
- [ ] All corner radius values noted
- [ ] All elevation/shadow specs listed

### 8.3 Assets

- [ ] App icon exported (all sizes)
- [ ] Splash screen designed
- [ ] Empty state illustrations created
- [ ] Icon set exported (if custom icons used)
- [ ] Play Store assets ready (screenshots, feature graphic)

### 8.4 Accessibility

- [ ] Contrast ratios verified (WCAG AA)
- [ ] Content descriptions written for key elements
- [ ] Touch targets meet 48dp minimum
- [ ] Focus order logical
- [ ] Color not sole indicator (use icons/labels too)

### 8.5 Interactivity

- [ ] All button states defined (default, pressed, disabled)
- [ ] All transitions specified (duration, easing)
- [ ] All gestures documented (tap, long-press, swipe)
- [ ] Haptic feedback points noted

